%description
/Overview/

The 'sparse-linear-algebra' library provides iterative linear solvers, matrix
decompositions, eigenvalue computations and related utilities. The user
interface is provided by the top-level module "Numeric.LinearAlgebra.Sparse":

' import Numeric.LinearAlgebra.Sparse '

Please refer to the README file for usage examples. .


